divs: Sighting DetailsMy daughter says that after she went from Philly over the Walt Whitman Bridge to New Jersey she spotted a light in the sky moving erratically. She had her camera with her and she took 4 pictures within a minute and a half. The first and last pictures don't seem to have anything that I can see. But the second and third pictures capture a UFO. Picture 114 clearly shows an orange colored UFO and picture 115 taken 18 seconds later show the UFO has a blue tone and is much further away. Since you only have three spots for download I will send the last 3 of the 4 pictures.
